  Locus:
    Page: 412
    Verse: 3
Tags:
  - Self
---
We seek satisfaction in the baubles of the world, yet we discover no
satisfaction at all, but only disappointment and despair. Finding no solace
anywhere, we at last turn to Reality where alone true satisfaction may be
found.
